{"_id":"0a06309e-a4ee-4a61-a7f4-b07de42518bd","type":"Item","name":"Binding 3: Elemental Binding","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Elemental Binding","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained/Permanent","cost":"2","description":"You bind a Fire, Cold, Energy, or Chem elemental â€“ this requires a fire, a shard of ice, a source of electricity, or a dangerous chemical compound. It is a level 2 Companion that is trained in attacks. It can use a Medium action to attack a single target in short range, dealing Light damage, or a Slow action to attack an area in short range, dealing Light damage. The damage dealt is of the corresponding type. It is immune to its own damage type. The elemental cannot be healed through any means.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"12964545-a766-4d7b-bafc-6c683732247c","type":"Item","name":"Binding 1: Minor Binding","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Minor Binding","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"Single","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained/Permanent","cost":"1","description":"You bind an everyday object or tool to work on its own at your direction. It is level 1 and trained in one skill of your choice related to its form (a rope may be trained in Athletics, a saw in Carpentry, etc). If you choose a weapon, it may make attacks when you direct to act in combat, unless it is a shield in which case it can actively defend on behalf of you or an ally in its area once per round.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"2c1321c9-3c09-46fb-ba40-3c08032c4f24","type":"Item","name":"Binding 5: Eviction Binding","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Eviction Binding","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"Maintained/Permanent","cost":"3","description":"You bind a persona into a living creature, granting the persona full control over their body. It keeps the same stats, skills, and abilities it had when it was alive. Track the original mind's Intuition separately from that of the newly bound persona. If the creature is in combat, you must make a new check each round of combat to maintain control over them. If you maintain control over a long period of time, you must also make a check at the start of each new day, dealing Light Intuition damage to the original mind on a success. This cannot deal Wounds, instead when the original mind's Intuition would go to zero it is extinguished, leaving them permanently under your control. This spell is nearly universally considered an evil and illegal act when used on intelligent beings.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"35ee46ba-84c1-4cef-9bfe-495dd037d92b","type":"Item","name":"Binding 1: Bind Persona","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Bind Persona","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"","range":"Adjacent","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You may only use this on a recently (within one minute) deceased living creature, absorbing its persona to form a persona crystal. The use of this spell is illegal in most places, and the creation and use of bound personas is considered worthy of capital punishment in many places.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"3971b2cb-f444-404d-b1f5-883e014ab657","type":"Item","name":"Binding 1: Binding Contract","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Binding Contract","rank":"1","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"Adjacent","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You cast this on a fully written contract prior to it being signed by one or more parties. For this spell to work, those who sign it must be aware of its contents. If the contract is later broken, an irremovable mark appears on the contract breaker's forehead and they burn one of each stat. Loopholes may be found within the contract with a Scribe check vs that of the writer.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"424d2dbb-d924-4ee4-8321-6a51651d5d53","type":"Item","name":"Binding 1: Direct Control","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Direct Control","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"Single","range":"Long","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"1","description":"You take direct control of a a bound creature you control, perceiving the world through its senses and using its physical stats but your mental stats and your skills. Any mind damage or burn to mental stats it would receive is received by you instead. You can continue to control it even without line of sight so long as you are within a very long range of it. You are incapacitated for the duration. When the spell ends the creature attempts to return to you if possible.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"95e36e3c-24c7-45d0-b881-d3f6bc736fd2","type":"Item","name":"Binding 5: Chains of Alistair","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Chains of Alistair","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"intuition","Target":"Single","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"Shimmering chains of pure persona bind your target, granting the Held condition using your Binding skill rather than Strength when they attempt to break free. Every time they fail to break free, they take Light Intuition damage.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"a2aefb99-3931-4344-8d28-c00b44b98079","type":"Item","name":"Binding 5: Self-Binding","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Self-Binding","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"Single","range":"Long","Duration":"","cost":"3","description":"You must have the Minor Binding, Elemental Binding, Grave Binding, or Eviction Binding spell to cast this. You cast one of those spells (with no additional Vim cost), but bind your own persona into the target rather than a bound or unbound persona. You may cast this spell without requiring an action if you would sustain a Critical Wound. You may target any bound creature you have created, in which case they do not defend.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"e3b4255a-c92b-4745-b9c3-1c3fab50e6fc","type":"Item","name":"Binding 3: Grave Binding","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Grave Binding","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"Maintained/Permanent","cost":"2","description":"You bind the corpse of a one-living being. It is a companion with stats equal to those it had when alive, and is trained only in attacks. It keeps the same attacks it had when alive. It is immune to Bleeding and Mind damage. It cannot be healed through any means, and disintegrates upon death.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"fd1c66c9-109c-400e-bfcf-db18c56c89d0","type":"Item","name":"Binding 3: Mindsend","system":{"skill":"Binding","name":"Mindsend","rank":"3","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"2","description":"You cast your persona out of your body to roam invisibly. You cannot interact with the world around you or cast spells but can see and hear as normal. You cannot be affected by any physical effects, but you cannot pass through solid materials. You take Light intelligence damage for each minute you spend outside your body.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
